{"tid":2433730,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"以〈R〉為名　BLACKPINK Rosé 首張個單預告連發！","createTime":"2021-03-05T05:28:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T08:50:55.000Z","uid":16659,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fcd6184b182826821da15d4f2037c31e133d1449","tid":2433730,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T05:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_1123b1f76124403b68c49a65e029bfb7/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-05/134069-898998.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_1123b1f76124403b68c49a65e029bfb7%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-05%2F134069-898998.png&h=27267e39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最近 Ros&eacute; 接連公開個人單曲〈R〉的預告照，今天也揭曉了首支主打歌名！<br />\n<br />\nYG Entertainment 今天（5 日）公開了 Ros&eacute; 首張個人單曲〈R〉的最新預告畫報，有別於前幾張畫報的粉紫色調，這次以黑底襯托散發銀白光芒的 Ros&eacute;，並用金字亮出主打歌名 &ldquo;On the Ground&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_55cf8ac4145d07ad62680d0495fbe816/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-05/134069-898999.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_55cf8ac4145d07ad62680d0495fbe816%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-05%2F134069-898999.jpeg&h=38236524&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRos&eacute; 先前早已在 BLACKPINK 的線上演唱會《THE SHOW》中表演過副主打歌 &ldquo;GONE&rdquo;，事先公開的預告片至今也已逾 4500 萬人觀看，顯示出各國粉絲對她的熱烈期待。<br />\n<br />\n目前 Ros&eacute; 已拍完 MV，YG 也預告這次砸下規模空前的製作費用，將帶來一部精彩的大作。另一方面，Ros&eacute; 將於 12 日下午 2 點（韓國時間）以唱片、黑膠和 KiT 三種形式發行〈R〉，在出道四年多後正式以個人之姿出道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_0859e2ec8f29d4ae06474dd793b8f4e2/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-05/134069-899000.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_0859e2ec8f29d4ae06474dd793b8f4e2%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-05%2F134069-899000.jpeg&h=e7569136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：YG Entertainment）"},{"pid":"8b457f464d985d83f15